  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    UK Foreign Secretary sets out ambition for closer relationship with India
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Dominic Raab met Minister for External Affairs Subrahmanyam Jaishankar in New Delhi today to set out the UK’s ambition for a strengthened UK-India relationship over the next 10 years.</p>

  </div>
</div>

